        <abstract> 
<p>Encloses diagram illustrating difference between <hi rend="italic">Chthamalus</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Balanus</hi>. Specimens sent. Finds no <hi rend="italic">Chthamalus</hi> in WT’s collection.</p>  
<p>Has read with much interest WT’s book [<hi rend="italic">The natural history of Ireland</hi>, vol. 1 (1849)].</p>  
<p>Recommends E. S. Dixon’s book [<hi rend="italic">Ornamental and domestic poultry; their history and management</hi> (1848)].</p> 
        </abstract>
